    <h1>Entropy and Diversity</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Tom Leinster · 2021 · Cambridge University Press</p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Prereqs: basic probability (what a distribution is). <a href="/reading/baez-fritz-2011/">🍞 Baez, Fritz, Leinster 2011</a> provides the entropy characterization.</p>

